text: MŠK Turany is a Slovak football team, based in the town of Turany. The club was founded in 1933. It currently plays in 1. trieda (6th tier in the Slovak football league system). == External links == *www.turany.sk ==References== Turany Category:Association football clubs established in 1933 Category:1933 establishments in Slovakia
